"A bag made from cut and woven strips of birchbark, not very flexible, has a "
"bone tog for fastening it closed, has a strap to wear over your torso"
msgstr "一個由切割並編織的樺樹皮條製成的袋子，不太柔韌，配有骨扣用於封口，並有可斜挎在身上的揹帶。"

