msgstr "一個A型框架揹包，附有一個樺樹皮袋用於儲存物品。有一個小環扣可用於攜帶斧頭或類似工具。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'a-frame birchbark backpack'}
#: .\aframes.json
msgid ""
"An A-Frame backpack with a looped cordage pouch fastened to it for storage. "
"There is a small loop for carrying am axe or similar"
msgstr "一個A型框架揹包，附有一個環狀繩索袋用於儲存物品。有一個小環扣可用於攜帶斧頭或類似工具。"

#: .\birch.json
msgid "birch water jug"
msgid_plural "birch water jugs"
msgstr[0] "樺樹水壺"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'birch water jug'}
#: .\birch.json
msgid ""
"A carefully made birch bark water jug with a lid, it is sealed with pine "
"pitch. It can hold 1.5 liters of water."
msgstr "一個精心製作的樺樹皮水壺，帶有蓋子，並用松脂密封。它可以容納1.5升水。"

#: .\birch.json
msgid "birch funnel"
msgid_plural "birch funnels"
msgstr[0] "樺樹漏斗"

#. ~ Use action done_message for {'str': 'birch funnel'}.
#: .\birch.json
msgid "You place the birch funnel, waiting to collect rain."
msgstr "你放置了樺樹漏斗，等待收集雨水。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'birch funnel'}
#: .\birch.json
msgid ""
"This is a small, birchbark funnel used to collect rainwater.  Use it outside"
" and place a container beneath it to collect water when it rains."
msgstr "這是一個用於收集雨水的小型樺樹皮漏斗。在室外使用它，並在下方放置容器，以便下雨時收集水。"

#: .\birch.json
msgid "birchbark funnel"
msgstr "樺樹皮漏斗"

#: .\bone-pickaxe.json
msgid "bone pickaxe"
msgid_plural "bone pickaxes"
msgstr[0] "骨制鎬"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bone pickaxe'}
#: .\bone-pickaxe.json
msgid ""
"This is a primitive pickaxe, traditionally made from antler or bone, and "
"fire-hardened for greater hardness.  It will wear out with use, but still "
"suitable for striking the earth."
msgstr "這是一把原始的鎬，傳統上由鹿角或骨頭製成，並通過火烤硬化以提高硬度。它會隨著使用而磨損，但仍適合挖掘土地。"

