#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Wild Living"
msgstr "野外生活"

#. ~ Description for Wild Living
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Expansion mod that brings more life and variety to the wilds. Merged with "
"Dried Fruits mod by Wayticus as well. Includes tons of new items with "
"recipes for enhanced wild living along with an ability to dry fruits, an "
"ability to grow various trees via planting them conveniently along with a "
"revamped, improved tree farm location with some new tropical trees. Link to "
"original - https://github.com/LambdaSix/Wild-Living"
msgstr ""
"為荒野帶來更多生機與多樣性的擴展模組。同時整合了Wayticus的乾果模組。包含大量新物品及其配方，以增強野外生活體驗，並具備乾燥水果的能力，以及通過便捷種植培育各種樹木的能力，還包含一個經過改進、優化的樹場地點，新增了一些熱帶樹木。原版鏈接"
" - https://github.com/LambdaSix/Wild-Living"

