#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid "date tree"
msgstr "椰棗樹"

#. ~ Description for date tree
#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid ""
"This is 'Phoenix dactylifera', commonly known as the date palm or even much "
"more commonly as the date tree, belonging to the 'Phoenix' genus, "
"naturalized in many tropical along with subtropical regions worldwide like "
"North Africa, Middle East, South Asia, that has been genetically engineered "
"to withstand New England's four seasons. It bears dates in the summer.  If "
"you examined the branches more closely, you could probably find some mature "
"dates.  You could also cut it down with the right tools."
msgstr ""
"這是'Phoenix "
"dactylifera'，通常被稱為棗椰樹或更常見的棗樹，屬於'Phoenix'屬，已在全球許多熱帶和亞熱帶地區歸化，如北非、中東、南亞，並經過基因工程改造以適應新英格蘭的四季。它在夏季結棗。如果你更仔細地檢查樹枝，可能會發現一些成熟的棗子。你也可以用合適的工具砍倒它。"

#. ~ Description for date tree
#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid ""
"This is 'Phoenix dactylifera', commonly known as the date palm or even much "
"more commonly as the date tree, belonging to the 'Phoenix' genus, "
"naturalized in many tropical along with subtropical regions worldwide like "
"North Africa, Middle East, South Asia, that has been genetically engineered "
"to withstand New England's four seasons. It bears dates in the summer.  "
"Looks like all the ripe dates have been picked.  You could also cut it down "
"with the right tools."
msgstr ""
"這是'Phoenix "
"dactylifera'，通常被稱為棗椰樹或更常見的棗樹，屬於'Phoenix'屬，已在全球許多熱帶和亞熱帶地區歸化，如北非、中東、南亞，並經過基因工程改造以適應新英格蘭的四季。它在夏季結棗。看起來所有成熟的棗子都已被採摘。你也可以用合適的工具砍倒它。"

#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid "fig tree"
msgstr "無花果樹"

#. ~ Description for fig tree
#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid ""
"This is 'Ficus carica', commonly known as fig tree, belonging to the 'Ficus'"
" genus, naturalized in many tropical along with subtropical regions like "
"Mediterranean, West Asia, South Asia, which is now widely grown throughout "
"the world, that has been genetically engineered to withstand New England's "
"four seasons. It bears figs in the summer.  If you examined the branches "
"more closely, you could probably find some mature figs.  You could also cut "
"it down with the right tools."
msgstr ""
"這是'Ficus "
"carica'，通常被稱為無花果樹，屬於'Ficus'屬，已在許多熱帶和亞熱帶地區歸化，如地中海、西亞、南亞，現已在全球廣泛種植，並經過基因工程改造以適應新英格蘭的四季。它在夏季結無花果。如果你更仔細地檢查樹枝，可能會發現一些成熟的無花果。你也可以用合適的工具砍倒它。"

