#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid "giant cockroach nymph"
msgid_plural "giant cockroach nymphs"
msgstr[0] "巨型蟑螂若蟲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant cockroach nymph'}
#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid "A baby mutant cockroach about the size of a rat."
msgstr "一隻幼年突變蟑螂，大小約如老鼠。"

#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid "dermatik larva"
msgid_plural "dermatik larvae"
msgstr[0] "皮蠅幼蟲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'dermatik larva', 'str_pl': 'dermatik larvae'}
#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid ""
"A fat white grub as big as a squirrel, with a pair of large, spadelike "
"mandibles."
msgstr "一條肥碩的白色蛆蟲，大小如松鼠，長有一對巨大的鏟狀顎。"

#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid "locust nymph"
msgid_plural "locust nymphs"
msgstr[0] "蝗蟲若蟲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'locust nymph'}
#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid ""
"A locust the size of a rabbit.  You'd hate to think what a swarm of these "
"could do."
msgstr "一隻兔子大小的蝗蟲。你不敢想象一群這樣的蝗蟲會造成什麼破壞。"

#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid "rattlesnake"
msgid_plural "rattlesnakes"
msgstr[0] "響尾蛇"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rattlesnake'}
#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid ""
"The timber rattlesnake is the most venomous viper native to New England.  "
"Climatic changes have extended its range far into the north."
msgstr "林響尾蛇是新英格蘭本土毒性最強的蝰蛇。氣候變化已將其活動範圍向北大幅擴展。"
